com.apriori.reflect.model

Interface Elements

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Elements

    public interface Elements
extends Elements
    An extension of the standard Elements interface that provides methods for inter-op with core reflection. For example, there are methods for querying for an Element corresponding to a java.lang.Class or a java.lang.reflect.Field.

    This interface provides factory methods to return instances backed by an annotation processing environment or by core reflection.

    See Also:
    fromProcessingEnvironment(ProcessingEnvironment), fromCoreReflection()
